      <title>中国经济疲软显现，全球石油前景面临考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/global-oil-outlook-faces-challenge-as-china-softness-surfaces</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年上半年，全球石油市场面临中国需求前景疲软的问题，这可能会给原油价格带来额外阻力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/global-oil-outlook-faces-challenge-as-china-softness-surfaces</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 06:14:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
